Subject: Re: [T2] Bolt size - early Bay fron bumper

VW N01024222
DIN Standard 8mm (1.25mm thread) x 22mm long x 13mm Hex Head Bolt.  2
per side, goes underneath.

VW 113 707 191
Chrome Carriage Bolt - connects Side Step Piece to Center Bumper
Blade.  Also 8mm thread.  Corresponding nut is N0110088 (8mm, 13mm
Hex) and Spring Washer N012282 (8mm).  I think there are 3 of each per
side.

